660 A.2d 1316 COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Appellee, v. Major FROST, Appellant. Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Submitted Dec. 7, 1994. Decided June 19, 1995. Bryan S. Walk, for M. Frost. Richard E. Guida, for Com.

Before: NIX, C.J., and FLAHERTY, ZAPPALA, CAPPY, CASTILLE and MONTEMURO, JJ.

ORDER

PER CURIAM.

Appeal DISMISSED as improvidently granted.

MONTEMURO, Senior Justice, is sitting by designation.
